<br>
All 5 of us take our classes seriously and are at the top of each class' game so to speak... not the best mind you, just with the best.<br>
<br>
mission at 3 am eastern?<br>
<br>
get arcana belt for monk's gnome cleric of gimpness.<br>
<br>
So we lazily plow through 3 waves of adds in arcana trial when at the break, the monk/cleric and our druid go ld.<br>
<br>
<br>
hmmm<br>
<br>
Liq tells the group &quot; hmmm we dead?&quot;<br>
<br>
rogue tells the group &quot;maybe!&quot;<br>
<br>
so the 4th wave pops, 3 normals and one special... comander or elite dunno...<br>
<br>
I spammed aoe slow til I knew it landed on all then twisted in mana and riz version 8.0 grabbing the loose adds.<br>
<br>
Warrior tanked the hard mob and no idea what the other 2 were on... all 3 of us, ping ponging like a pack of clueless wizzys prolly.<br>
<br>
<br>
I whacked song of shields at start<br>
<br>
I clicked epic 1.5<br>
<br>
mass rogue and warrior discs went BLING all fight but spiked on epic click<br>
<br>
I wasted dance of blades to help get aggro on a second add and spammed el aoe slow.<br>
<br>
I discdanced at 15% hp for the lovable low hp aggo and faded the last add living add at half  hp.<br>
<br>
got the 2 mins left warning and the last mob died right after.<br>
<br>
right then the druid poped back in and came back to a bard at 7%, warrior at 30% and a rogue at ~50%<br>
<br>
druid was confused.<br>
<br>
We got the 1 min left mark, the monk logged on soon after then got the 30 second mark.... memed my targeted slow loadout and occ slowed the boss who was at ~50% hp when the monk's cleric came in<br>
<br>
gg gnome on belt of the uber twink!!!!!<br>
<br>
<br>
Fear the bard war rogue!<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Cheers!<br>
-Liq<br>
